American TeleSource gets credit facility from IBM . Privately held American TeleSource International Inc on Tuesday said that through its Mexican subsidiary ATSI Mexico SA de CV , a $ 1 . 725 million credit facility has been secured with International Business Machines Corp ' s Mexican unit . ATSI said the credit facility will assist the company in the purchase of U . S . - standard intelligent pay telephones for installation in Mexico . Intelligent pay phones are capable of accepting credit cards calling card an coins , the firm said . The compamny said it plans to install 11 , 000 pay phones over the next five years . 
